headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Visit the Test Track to Try Out the Karin Sultan Classic, Obey Tailgater S, and Übermacht Cypher
content: Pay the LS Car Meet’s Test Track a visit to give the Karin Sultan Classic, Obey Tailgater S, and Übermacht Cypher a spin around the columns and see how they handle the rigors of a Scramble or slam the pedal to the metal in a Time Trial.
